    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "USS use E52142A, it needs a clock input on CLKREF pin. This clock should be generated by SAIL_IO. Next table shows clock requirement."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [],
      "rows": [
        [
          "",
          "Min",
          "Typ",
          "Max",
          "Unit"
        ],
        [
          "Duty cycle of the CLKREF signal",
          "40",
          "50",
          "60",
          "%"
        ],
        [
          "Clock reference input frequency range",
          "499.5",
          "500",
          "500.5",
          "KHz"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Clock control unit can generate clock by specific SAIL_IOs."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But MCAL from Qualcomm can't support PWM module."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. Port configuration"
    },
